NK041(di)031:2: deng gi rgyu sbyor yon bdag la //
NK041(di)031:3: sngon gyi lan chags 'brel ba yis //
NK041(di)031:4: bla la brkus sam gzhom srid na //
NK041(di)031:5: bla glud gser skyems 'di bzhes la //
NK041(di)031:6: bzung ba thong la bcings pa khrol //
NK041(di)031:7: bsdams pa klod la mnan pa theg /
NK041(di)031:8: zhi ba chen po'i ngang la bzhugs //
NK041(di)031:10: rgyu sbyor mi bu rin chen 'di'i //
NK041(di)031:11: bla la brkus sam gzhom srid na //
NK041(di)031:12: nam mkha' khams kyi mdangs dang ldan //
NK041(di)031:13: rgyang bu de ni 'phan bzang dang //
NK041(di)031:14: pho gdong mo gdong 'gro shes dang //
NK041(di)031:15: ngar mi'i lus la rgyan cha can //
NK041(di)031:16: bla glud gser skyems 'di bzhes la //
NK041(di)031:17: bzung ba thong la bcings pa khrol //
NK041(di)031:18: bsdams pa klod la mnan pa theg /
NK041(di)031:19: zhi ba chen po'i ngang la bzhugs //
NK041(di)031:20: phyogs bcu'i gdon gyi skabs su /
NK041(di)031:21: khar sang kha yi nyi ma la //
NK041(di)031:22: rgyu sbyor mi bu rin chen 'di'i //
NK041(di)031:23: bla la brkus sam gzhom srid na //
